{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "d0e1f203-1a2f-082d-72a2-b28100818b9c",
    "name": "Employee Management API",
    "description": "Complete collection for Employee Management System APIs with JWT Authentication.\n\n🔐 AUTHENTICATION:\n- Register users (automatically creates employee profile)\n- Login to get JWT token\n- Use Bearer token for secured endpoints\n\n📱 REGISTRATION REQUIREMENTS:\n- Name: Minimum 3 characters\n- Email: Valid email format\n- Password: Minimum 6 characters\n- Phone Number: Exactly 10 digits\n- Role: USER or ADMIN\n\n👥 EMPLOYEE MANAGEMENT:\n- Paginated employee listing\n- Get own profile (/me)\n- CRUD operations with role-based access\n- ADMIN: Full access\n- USER: Read access + own profile management\n\n📧 FEATURES:\n- Async welcome email sending\n- Duplicate prevention (email & phone)\n- Input validation\n- Comprehensive error handling",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Authentication endpoints for user registration and login. JWT tokens are automatically saved to collection variables.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"phoneNumber\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"role\": \"USER\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "register"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if(jsonData.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", jsonData.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Employees",
      "description": "Employee management endpoints with role-based access control.\n\n🔐 ACCESS CONTROL:\n- ADMIN: Full CRUD operations on all employees\n- USER: Read operations + manage own profile only\n\n📄 PAGINATION:\n- Get All Employees supports: ?page=0&size=10&sortBy=id\n- Sorting options: id, firstName, lastName, email, department, salary",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Employees",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/employees?page=0&size=10&sortBy=id",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "employees"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "0",
                  "description": "Page number (0-based)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "size",
                  "value": "10",
                  "description": "Number of items per page"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sortBy",
                  "value": "id",
                  "description": "Sort field (id, firstName, lastName, email, department, salary)"
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
